they're going to crush us.

331
00:20:04,699 --> 00:20:06,659
It means we’ll never be able to beat them.

332
00:20:07,929 --> 00:20:10,339
YGN is doing various PR work

333
00:20:10,429 --> 00:20:12,949
as well as advertising
