336
00:20:18,199 --> 00:20:21,689
Yes, we've had a couple new hires
that couldn't endure their training

337
00:20:21,989 --> 00:20:24,659
and wound up quitting their jobs.

338
00:20:24,889 --> 00:20:25,889
Why do you ask?

339
