340
00:20:36,779 --> 00:20:38,319
Then, he tells me not to be one.

341
00:20:38,409 --> 00:20:41,219
I asked him to give me a reason,
but he didn't tell me anything.

342
00:20:42,129 --> 00:20:43,339
