343
00:20:43,429 --> 00:20:45,889
No, Dal-Po is the weird one.

344
00:20:46,829 --> 00:20:48,419
No one wants to take my side.

345
00:20:48,509 --> 00:20:51,459
My dad, Dal-Po, and my mom...
