346
00:20:51,549 --> 00:20:52,909
How does this even happen?

347
00:20:52,999 --> 00:20:56,089
Is the world going to end or something
if a Pinocchio becomes a reporter?

348
00:20:56,179 --> 00:20:57,529
No, that won't happen.

349
00:20:57,829 --> 00:20:58,669
Never.

350
00:20:59,549 --> 00:21:02,449
If it hadn't been for these hiccups,
things wouldn't have gotten this bad.

351
00:21:02,539 --> 00:21:04,939
Come on, hiccups are considered cute.

352
00:21:05,539 --> 00:21:07,939
