00:21:10,599 --> 00:21:12,389
My goodness. You're right.

356
00:21:13,279 --> 00:21:15,809
It's a relief that I only resort
to hiccuping not farting.

357
00:21:18,309 --> 00:21:19,559
That's comforting to hear.

358
00:21:19,849 --> 00:21:20,689
Really?

359
00:21:21,059 --> 00:21:22,059
That's good to hear.

360
00:21:23,649 --> 00:21:24,669
Thank you.

361
00:21:24,789 --> 00:21:27,089
After all the talking I just did,
I feel better...

362
00:21:28,799 --> 00:21:30,249
...as if I went to confession.

363
00:21:30,579 --> 00:21:32,429
I enjoy listening to you talk.

364
00:21:33,609 --> 00:21:35,209
You look better than I thought.

365
00:21:40,839 --> 00:21:43,679
I thought you'd be moping around
after failed at all the stations,

366
00:21:43,959 --> 00:21:45,169
but you look quite okay.

367
00:21:58,019 --> 00:21:59,699
How did you know that I'd be here?

368
00:22:00,489 --> 00:22:02,679
You had written it all down
in your cover letter,

369
00:22:03,059 --> 00:22:04,669
as if you wanted me to come to visit.

370
00:22:04,849 --> 00:22:05,949
You even wrote your address.

371
00:22:06,409 --> 00:22:07,879
That was because...

372
00:22:09,999 --> 00:22:11,733
-That was...
-I'll just get right to the point.

373
00:22:13,089 --> 00:22:14,949
I'm not interested in hearing
whatever you say.

374
00:22:15,769 --> 00:22:17,319
Your desire to become a reporter...

375
00:22:18,689 --> 00:22:19,899
do you still feel that way?

376
00:22:20,309 --> 00:22:21,374
Reporter?

377
00:22:25,129 --> 00:22:27,289
-Why?
-We've had some slots open up.

378
00:22:28,239 --> 00:22:29,179
Interested?

379
00:22:30,799 --> 00:22:32,489
Seems you regret your decision?

380
00:22:32,759 --> 00:22:34,199
Or am I fail but came a close second?

381
00:22:34,289 --> 00:22:35,129
Or...

382
00:22:38,649 --> 00:22:39,739
