433
00:26:09,249 --> 00:26:10,639
But more than anything else,

434
00:26:11,069 --> 00:26:13,349
what would happen if a Pinocchio
become a reporter?

435
00:26:13,849 --> 00:26:14,739
And also...

436
00:26:14,829 --> 00:26:15,949
My son.

437
00:26:16,129 --> 00:26:17,539
You're acting very strange lately.

438
00:26:17,629 --> 00:26:19,569
-How so?
-You're curious...

439
00:26:19,809 --> 00:26:21,091
...about way too many things lately.

440
00:26:22,469 --> 00:26:23,469
Am I?

441
00:26:24,729 --> 00:26:25,719
That's weird.

442
00:26:27,089 --> 00:26:28,269
Drink it.

443
00:26:28,429 --> 00:26:29,269
Okay.

444
00:26:31,799 --> 00:26:32,729
