447
00:26:40,339 --> 00:26:41,179
There you are.

448
00:26:41,329 --> 00:26:42,529
You surprised me.

449
00:26:42,769 --> 00:26:43,909
Why were you doing that?

450
00:26:44,129 --> 00:26:45,299
I have a lot on my mind.

451
00:26:45,399 --> 00:26:47,239
And I have a lot of decisions
to make, too.

452
00:26:47,359 --> 00:26:49,059
Have you made your decision, then?

453
00:26:49,489 --> 00:26:50,329
Yeah.

454
00:26:50,509 --> 00:26:53,779
I've organized almost everything,
so just check kimbap expiration dates.

455
00:26:53,889 --> 00:26:54,879
Bye.

456
00:27:26,249 --> 00:27:27,089
Crazy little thing.

457
00:27:27,259 --> 00:27:28,719
