502
00:31:32,099 --> 00:31:33,459
That's not allowed to happen.

503
00:31:34,169 --> 00:31:35,069
Because we're family.

504
00:31:41,389 --> 00:31:43,029
Don't worry, because my feelings...

505
00:31:44,429 --> 00:31:46,269
