515
00:32:38,019 --> 00:32:38,949
Come in.

516
00:32:41,429 --> 00:32:42,269
What is it?

517
00:32:43,769 --> 00:32:45,559
No, it's nothing.

518
00:32:45,999 --> 00:32:49,184
There's a grandmother looking for a place
for her and her grandson a while back.

519
00:32:49,274 --> 00:32:51,054
So I helped her with no charge.

520
00:32:51,145 --> 00:32:54,146
Then, she came by a while ago
and gave me this cake as a thank you.

521
00:32:54,237 --> 00:32:55,793
Really? What a perfect timing!

522
00:32:57,028 --> 00:32:58,001
Use fork.

523
00:32:58,454 --> 00:33:00,394
I'll just wash my hands after.

524
00:33:00,564 --> 00:33:03,624
